{"tid":335680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好介意人講大話","createTime":"2017-07-25T18:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T09:08:56.000Z","uid":60670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3832c5573a2711c9269ac9fd037a7ab8c60db286","tid":335680,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:25:11.000Z","msg":"無論係男朋友定朋友都好，我地好唔鍾意佢地呃我，俾人瞞住嘅感覺一啲都唔好受。<br />\n以為自己真誠咁對人，人就會真誠咁對返自己，其實所有野都係假，成個傻仔咁交哂個心岀嚟。<br />\n自從發現男朋友一而再再而三咁呃我之後（唔係綠帽），無辦法開心返，就算我幾努力扮都好，夜晚得返自己一個都係會喊。<br />\n點先可以揾返對佢嘅信任呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家失望到谷底會諗係咪自己有問題<br />\n其實唔介意咁多嘅話根本唔洗咁傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6ed8ec6dc885d9706f29dec12b916655a11049","tid":335680,"uid":68864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"未傾過咪同佢講<br />\n話過都係咁就冷戰啦 之後有三個可能<br />\n一係分手<br />\n二係氹返你 過一排又重犯 無限loop到你頂唔順走<br />\n三係氹返你 認真改過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b25088f8a8f253632ac8a1a86d18e49c56194a","tid":335680,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢穿左仲扮野先肉酸"},{"pid":"2f6ce69cde3e82d199ba92ab706cd45d0fe6fffb","tid":335680,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"我唔介意人講大話，但唔該呃我一世"},{"pid":"54bb64ce1f3f7f0bf52da882701d47eabe5a5a1d","tid":335680,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未傾過咪同佢講<br />\n話過都係咁就冷戰啦 之後有三個可能<br />\n一係分手<br />\n二係氹返你 過一排又重犯 無限loop到你頂唔順走<br />\n三係氹返你 認真改過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家嘅結果係三<br />\n不過我唔知信唔信好<br />\n信任無左真係好難有返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25eb3eea3927fef90367ad25499a515c2b791f37","tid":335680,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢穿左仲扮野先肉酸</blockquote><br />\n佢會一路扮<br />\n扮到我講到好清楚佢瞞左啲咩先認<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1365fecfcec4aedfac21a780c1e7eaea068499","tid":335680,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔介意人講大話，但唔該呃我一世</blockquote><br />\n當你發現左個陣唔會好痛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1e907af71c3b46143ec248718a888d5687fb1b","tid":335680,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔介意人講大話，但唔該呃我一世</blockquote><br />\n當你發現左個陣唔會好痛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以做戲就做好啲"},{"pid":"511bcde7802cc87dd78afd2b367f395991542009","tid":335680,"uid":35537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔介意人講大話，但唔該呃我一世</blockquote><br />\n當你發現左個陣唔會好痛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以做戲就做好啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有誰不是戲子？<br />\n<br />\n放低過後再做另一場戲啦！"},{"pid":"619608bc9e0d6b9c4dad377495d20e524253a234","tid":335680,"uid":60670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔介意人講大話，但唔該呃我一世</blockquote><br />\n當你發現左個陣唔會好痛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以做戲就做好啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有誰不是戲子？<br />\n<br />\n放低過後再做另一場戲啦！</blockquote><br />\n你瞞住我<br />\n我亦瞞住我<br />\n太合襯"}]}